---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Contacto - Playauto">
  <section class="bg-gray-800 mt-16">
    <div class=" mx-auto px-6 py-12 xl:px-20">
        <div class="md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-6 md:mb-0 xl:mx-20">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-100">Contacto</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mt-4">Para más información o si tienes alguna pregunta, por favor, no dudes en contactarnos.</p>
                <div class="mt-8">
                    <p class="flex items-center text-gray-300 mb-2">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot w-6 h-6 fill-current text-sky-800 mr-3 mt-2"></i>
                        Dirección: San Lorenzo, Central, Paraguay.
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex items-center text-gray-300 mb-2">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-phone w-6 h-6 fill-current text-sky-800 mr-3 mt-2"></i>
                        Teléfono: +595 983 882017
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex items-center text-gray-300 mb-6">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope w-6 h-6 fill-current text-sky-800 mr-3 mt-2"></i>
                        Email: bytechpy@gmail.com
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-center md:justify-start space-x-3 mt-5">
                        <a href="https://wa.me/595983882017" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 items-center justify-center inline-flex rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg  text-white bg-sky-800 hover:drop-shadow-lg cursor-pointer transition ease-in duration-300"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i></a>
                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bytechpy/" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 items-center justify-center inline-flex rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg  text-white bg-sky-800 hover:drop-shadow-lg cursor-pointer transition ease-in duration-300"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/bytechparaguay/" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 items-center justify-center inline-flex rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg  text-white bg-sky-800 hover:drop-shadow-lg cursor-pointer transition ease-in duration-300"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                      </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 bg-slate-900 p-6 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-100 font-semibold mb-6">Envíanos un mensaje</h3>
                <form action="https://formsubmit.co/bytechpy@gmail.com" method="POST">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-gray-400">Nombre</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Tu nombre" class="w-full px-4 py-2 mt-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-800" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-gray-400">Email</label>
                        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Tu email" class="w-full px-4 py-2 mt-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-800" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-gray-400">Telefono</label>
                        <input type="number" name="number" placeholder="Tu numero" class="w-full px-4 py-2 mt-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-800" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-gray-400">Mensaje</label>
                        <textarea name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Tu mensaje" class="w-full px-4 py-2 mt-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-800" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-end mt-6">
                        <button type="submit" class="px-6 py-2 leading-5 text-white transition-colors duration-200 transform bg-sky-800 rounded-md hover:bg-sky-800 focus:outline-none focus:bg-sky-800">Enviar</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</Layout>